Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:03.81,title01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(550,0)\shad1}Kamakura
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.27,0:00:06.82,title01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(630,0)\fs14\fscx120}10:10 AM
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.60,0:00:08.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we keep going up this hill...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.10,0:00:11.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll get to see a famous temple that's surrounded by hydrangeas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.56,0:00:14.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really, it's a beautiful sight to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.32,0:00:17.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.48,0:00:18.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There aren't any flowers here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.94,0:00:20.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.28,0:00:21.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did I get it wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.95,0:00:22.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.26,0:00:34.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Love is eternal, labyrinths are mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:35.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saturday nights are for mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.76,0:00:38.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three brothers, unable to understand their parent's love...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.01,0:00:41.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fight over an inheritance, resulting in an unfortunate case!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.39,0:00:42.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.96,0:00:44.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.74,0:00:46.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.79,0:02:38.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what happened!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.17,0:02:39.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is everything all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.42,0:02:40.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.34,0:02:47.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.18,0:02:48.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hell are you doing over there!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.55,0:02:51.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.81,0:02:55.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell me what that gunshot was about!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.10,0:02:56.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.65,0:02:59.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fuck off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.15,0:03:01.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:21.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.21,0:03:23.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The blood's already dried.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.09,0:03:28.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's still warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.72,0:03:29.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, why...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:33.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.81,0:03:35.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like some sort of crystalline substance...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.64,0:03:38.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn, that guy was quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.18,0:03:39.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.23,0:03:40.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.19,0:03:42.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you find?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.52,0:03:44.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:45.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.46,0:03:51.20,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The victim is Yaguchi Hisaemon{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, 70 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.69,0:03:51.20,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Yaguchi Hisaemon (70)\NProperty Investor
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.45,0:03:55.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was the owner of this house and was quite a property investor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:58.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was shot directly in the chest and died soon thereafter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.91,0:04:00.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was the fatal shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.46,0:04:03.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The weapon was that rifle over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.04,0:04:06.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.00,0:04:08.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You all happen to be the witnesses, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.80,0:04:09.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.76,0:04:10.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.63,0:04:11.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you doing back in Kamakura again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.34,0:04:14.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just sightseeingâ€”sightseeing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.14,0:04:16.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These kids said they wanted to watch the hydrangeas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.26,0:04:17.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Yokomizo, one moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.44,0:04:23.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.52,0:04:26.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it true that my dad's dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.94,0:04:28.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:29.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, and you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.93,0:04:31.88,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'm his oldest son, Rokurou.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.90,0:04:33.20,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,What's your occupation?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:34.99,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'm a film director.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:34.99,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\be3}Yaguchi Rokurou (42)\NFirst-Born Son
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.66,0:04:37.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Film director?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.12,0:04:38.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Never heard of one by that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.79,0:04:43.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Regardless, have you figured out whodunit?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.37,0:04:45.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before that, at 6:00 this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.71,0:04:46.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.96,0:04:51.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it was almost 10:00 when we heard the gunshot...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.01,0:04:53.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was killed long before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:54.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.68,0:04:55.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.64,0:04:57.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to autopsy, his time of death is around...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.39,0:04:58.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.14,0:04:59.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.68,0:05:00.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.85,0:05:03.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, the time of death is around 6:00?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.15,0:05:06.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, the gunshot we heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.52,0:05:08.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was that to throw us off the scent of the real time of death?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.10,0:05:10.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, even that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.86,0:05:12.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was in Tokushima.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.99,0:05:15.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went to Tokushima seeking inspiration for my new film.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.37,0:05:19.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I checked out of the hotel at about half-past 6:00...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.45,0:05:22.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And by the time I made it back to Tokyo, it was already after 10:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.91,0:05:24.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.75,0:05:27.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I also kept the stub to my boarding pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.21,0:05:28.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.38,0:05:32.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:33.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Check this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.92,0:05:34.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.18,0:05:37.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, did Hisaemon{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} live here alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:39.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.60,0:05:41.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He used to have servants here looking after him, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.89,0:05:43.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He laid them off a half-year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.14,0:05:46.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.35,0:05:48.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To think he'd go this far just to save money...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.19,0:05:51.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a stingy father he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:54.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He decided not to keep servants, despite owning a large house?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.45,0:05:57.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have any other family members?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.03,0:05:58.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two younger brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.78,0:06:02.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's rightâ€”they may know something about this incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.79,0:06:07.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, of course, I wouldn't know if they'd tell the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:13.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, we know you're in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.01,0:06:13.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get out here right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:15.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Return the money or else!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.89,0:06:21.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who're you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.47,0:06:24.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some punks looking for trouble!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.06,0:06:26.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.14,0:06:27.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our apologies, Big Boss Yokomizo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.65,0:06:31.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys are still doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.19,0:06:34.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.53,0:06:36.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.78,0:06:42.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yaguchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.16,0:06:44.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yaguchi Akehiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.79,0:06:45.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.83,0:06:47.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have things to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.41,0:06:52.55,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The police?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.58,0:06:53.50,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.09,0:06:53.50,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\be3}Yaguchi Akihiko (37)\NSecond-Born Son
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.51,0:06:58.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Around 6:00, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.76,0:07:01.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was at this family restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.26,0:07:07.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To get to my dad's house from there,\Nit'd take about an hour even by car.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.14,0:07:10.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The money it took to open this shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.23,0:07:12.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your father was the one who covered it, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.27,0:07:16.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And even beyond that, you still received money from him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.57,0:07:19.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until he recently refused to give you any more, isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.32,0:07:21.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who told you that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.91,0:07:24.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your elder brother, Rokurou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.70,0:07:25.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.66,0:07:26.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:30.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My brother's the one who relied on Dad to fund his movies!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.46,0:07:34.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But since he didn't give him much, he still had to take out loans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.38,0:07:41.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, the company I ran went bankrupt recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:46.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And my father, who had always supported me\Nfinancially, refused to bail me out just like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.60,0:07:50.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, let's talk about what you did at 6:00 this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.54,0:07:53.01,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,That... That early?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.03,0:07:54.65,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Of course, I was still asleep around 6:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:54.65,CharCard - 2,,0,0,0,,Yaguchi Kimio (32)\NThird-Born Son
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.98,0:07:57.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.19,0:07:58.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:02.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, prior to the incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.74,0:08:06.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was someone who witnessed you at the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:15.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Care to explain that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.96,0:08:17.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.59,0:08:17.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.55,0:08:19.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.51,0:08:21.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went to... my father's house...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:23.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.47,0:08:25.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For... the money...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.18,0:08:26.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With good intentions?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.43,0:08:27.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.31,0:08:31.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I tried to steal some...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.02,0:08:31.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.15,0:08:33.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It isn't like I heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.06,0:08:36.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't get this safe open...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.98,0:08:38.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.44,0:08:39.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.19,0:08:42.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.95,0:08:47.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kimio!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:52.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a pathetic man you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.04,0:08:54.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To think you would act like a thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.25,0:08:55.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was told by Akihiko that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.59,0:08:58.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akihiko, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.67,0:09:01.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dammit, you freeloaders never take responsibility and grow up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.30,0:09:05.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not a freeloader!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.39,0:09:08.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.35,0:09:09.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.97,0:09:12.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, I went to see my brother Akihiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.27,0:09:15.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.27,0:09:15.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.65,0:09:18.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad caught me stealing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.65,0:09:20.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:23.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I even taught you step-by-step how to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.24,0:09:24.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Step-by-step"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.36,0:09:26.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What I saw wasn't what we expected at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.32,0:09:27.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad's safe was so sturdy there was no way to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.49,0:09:29.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.62,0:09:30.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:32.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, that bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.75,0:09:34.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When'd he buy a safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.25,0:09:36.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.00,0:09:36.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.63,0:09:38.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You still want to steal it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:39.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.88,0:09:42.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a portion of the green to shut you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.30,0:09:44.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.72,0:09:49.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that safe is really that sturdy, I've gotta prepare some tools...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.81,0:09:54.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was at 6:00 this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.07,0:10:03.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.32,0:10:05.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To think you two were going to rob from Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:07.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Akihiko who told me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.66,0:10:08.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't blame me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.91,0:10:10.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you really did!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.37,0:10:11.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What, disbanding right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.95,0:10:13.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.75,0:10:15.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akihiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.08,0:10:19.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until 5:45 this morning, you claimed you were in a restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.38,0:10:22.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This has since been confirmed by the waitress and several customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.96,0:10:24.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.84,0:10:29.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afterward, you went to a discount shop nearby to buy some items.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.18,0:10:32.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A crowbar, an electric drill...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.27,0:10:36.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A number of witnesses confirmed this for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.52,0:10:38.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I remembered, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.60,0:10:39.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at your right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.40,0:10:42.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.90,0:10:46.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine, I did come to steal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.11,0:10:48.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I didn't kill Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.11,0:10:49.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I arrived, Dad was already...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.20,0:10:52.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.24,0:10:55.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.08,0:10:56.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, this is my{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ce...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.92,0:11:03.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It really was a strong safe, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.13,0:11:05.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I tried my best and still couldn't get it open.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.42,0:11:06.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.59,0:11:08.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How's this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.97,0:11:14.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, the gunshot we heard at that time was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.18,0:11:16.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was me, but the rifle couldn't beat that safe either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.77,0:11:20.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The time of death was around 6:00 this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.65,0:11:21.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.94,0:11:24.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The eldest brother, Rokurou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, was in Tokushima...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.23,0:11:28.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While Akihiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, the second youngest\Nbrother, and Kimio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, the youngest...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.28,0:11:31.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were at a family restaurant an hour's drive away by car.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:34.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hisaemon{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was shot at close range...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.54,0:11:38.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After seeing the culprit wielding a rifle right before his eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.16,0:11:39.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't he try to escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.75,0:11:41.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.67,0:11:44.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The white crystalline substance...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.38,0:11:48.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just what was that, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.06,0:11:59.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.73,0:12:01.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aside from the body...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.19,0:12:04.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What else do you notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.11,0:12:05.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or, not notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.49,0:12:08.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.53,0:12:13.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad's antique collections are gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.28,0:12:17.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd bet it was our older brother that snatched them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.79,0:12:19.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:22.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet you stole them when you came to break into the safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.96,0:12:27.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim recently discontinued financial aid for his sons...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.38,0:12:31.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He also dismissed his servants six months ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.22,0:12:33.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then his antiques were gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.39,0:12:35.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.64,0:12:37.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, that safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.60,0:12:43.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, we found this item in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.06,0:12:46.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It appears to be a webcam.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.15,0:12:49.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who planted that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.53,0:12:51.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're a pro when it comes to cameras, big bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.45,0:12:52.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.74,0:12:54.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you saying I did that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.32,0:12:54.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.08,0:12:57.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.58,0:13:01.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone, we've come across further information.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.66,0:13:03.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So please, come back over to the other room again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.50,0:13:05.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, Detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.33,0:13:07.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you open that safe for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.34,0:13:13.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.30,0:13:15.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In this position...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.89,0:13:21.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Mr. Detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.23,0:13:26.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where was that stuffed eagle originally?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.15,0:13:27.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.52,0:13:28.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.65,0:13:31.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See that dust mark?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:33.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think the eagle was placed here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.99,0:13:36.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And fell off while the victim was struggling with the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:43.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rokurou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, I have received a report\Nfrom the Tokushima Police Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.79,0:13:44.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.96,0:13:47.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was in Tokushima staying at a hotel, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.04,0:13:49.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it was witnessed...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.75,0:13:52.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That a man wearing a hat and sunglasses like yours was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.84,0:13:55.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.68,0:13:57.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, how should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.93,0:14:02.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard the guest refused to remove his hat\Nand sunglasses even while inside his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.60,0:14:05.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because this is my trademark style...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:07.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't take these off in front of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.52,0:14:09.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, since no one saw your face...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.57,0:14:12.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't say that guest was you, can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.57,0:14:14.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.74,0:14:18.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, that guest's checkout time wasn't until tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.66,0:14:21.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he suddenly decided to leave this morning, I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.24,0:14:24.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps he already knew that Hisaemon{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.87,0:14:26.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was dead at that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.87,0:14:29.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This morning in a haste, that must be it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.71,0:14:33.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The loans you borrowed were huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.92,0:14:39.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, you said you had already\Nsecured a way to pay off all those debts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.39,0:14:40.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.39,0:14:42.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So big bro really did kill Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.39,0:14:43.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.35,0:14:46.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, the person who went to Tokushima was a double that you hired?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.73,0:14:52.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then you used that online webcam to monitor this study...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.44,0:14:55.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to obtain the code for the safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.78,0:14:57.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:15:00.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You saw Kimio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} attempt his robbery over that camera...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.37,0:15:06.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And decided to kill Hisaemon{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and frame Kimio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.71,0:15:11.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because even if you couldn't open the safe,\Nyou could inherit more money this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.71,0:15:12.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Big bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.63,0:15:13.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:16.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's complete nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:19.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You broke into the house this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.30,0:15:21.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And killed Hisaemon{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} in his study.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.30,0:15:24.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since there aren't any neighboring houses nearby...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.81,0:15:27.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was no one around to hear the gunshot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.52,0:15:33.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you ordered your double to return\Nand hand over the ticket stub to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.57,0:15:37.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That way, you could appear here as if nothing happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.07,0:15:37.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.99,0:15:40.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wrong, wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.61,0:15:41.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.82,0:15:43.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where the hell are we wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.03,0:15:45.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Spit it out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:51.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.38,0:15:54.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rokurou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.84,0:15:57.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I advise you to tell the truth for your own sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.13,0:16:00.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't, you'll be made the culprit by mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.01,0:16:01.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.80,0:16:07.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hisaemon{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s death was actually an unfortunate accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.77,0:16:08.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.93,0:16:09.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.02,0:16:11.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by "accident"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.44,0:16:14.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Recall the position where the body fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.65,0:16:18.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Judging from that position...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.44,0:16:20.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Hisaemon{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was shot...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.61,0:16:26.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He would be standing about a foot away from the cabinet, facing the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.12,0:16:32.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It isn't possible to stand in front of him\Nand shoot him in the chest like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.00,0:16:37.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, consider the stuffed eagle that fell next to the victim's foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.05,0:16:41.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that branch the eagle was perched onâ€”it was broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.09,0:16:43.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it was, but what does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.30,0:16:45.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rokurou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.89,0:16:47.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You actually witnessed the entire scene, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.39,0:16:50.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On that webcam of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.94,0:16:55.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.73,0:16:57.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.32,0:17:00.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seeing is believing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.74,0:17:05.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.99,0:17:07.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.66,0:17:16.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After Kimio fled, Dad sat there like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.88,0:17:18.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.84,0:17:20.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it a heart attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:29.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the trigger got{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} tan{\r}gled on the eagle's\Nbranch and caused the gun to misfire.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.43,0:17:31.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.56,0:17:35.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The way Dad died wasn't by murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.52,0:17:36.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.94,0:17:37.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:40.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you had this on video all along, why didn't you show us earlier!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.86,0:17:43.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He tried to make Akihiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Kimio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.49,0:17:45.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Appear to be murderers...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.45,0:17:46.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to keep them from getting the inheritance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.53,0:17:48.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.33,0:17:51.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was why Rokurou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} hurriedly returned from Tokushima.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.33,0:17:54.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before the body was discovered..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.71,0:18:01.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He planned to recover the webcam and plant fake evidence\Nthat made it seem the crime was committed by his brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.59,0:18:05.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, before he could, we discovered the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.14,0:18:07.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You bastard, how could you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.51,0:18:11.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At least I proved you two innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:13.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should thank me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.18,0:18:14.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For what!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.02,0:18:15.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, what becomes of our share of the inheritance?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:16.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.69,0:18:17.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Regardless, just get that safe open!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.56,0:18:20.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For the two that act like robbers...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.77,0:18:23.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think you have the right to inherit anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.36,0:18:24.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.53,0:18:26.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. "Spy Camera" Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.24,0:18:27.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't just keep everything yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.57,0:18:28.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Knock it off already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.95,0:18:33.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you still not figured out Hisaemon{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s feelings!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.16,0:18:35.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad's feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.12,0:18:38.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After Kimio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} fled...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.42,0:18:39.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He sat in front of the safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:41.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Hisaemon{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.67,0:18:42.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wept in sorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.38,0:18:45.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Wept"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.84,0:18:47.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad did?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.09,0:18:49.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could you know such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.85,0:18:53.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On Hisaemon{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s collar and chest...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.22,0:18:56.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Traces of a white, crystalline substance can be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.06,0:18:59.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is most likely...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.56,0:19:00.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Salt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.15,0:19:04.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The tears ended up drying out on his clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.15,0:19:06.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And left traces of salt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.03,0:19:12.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To have left salt crystals after his tears dried,\Nhe must have shed a lot of them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.45,0:19:14.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.66,0:19:18.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He must have cried in deep sorrow, and out of great embarrassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.00,0:19:21.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He loved and pampered you all so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.71,0:19:25.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And yet you still cannot take care of yourselves or take responsibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:31.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was due to the pampering that he\Nfelt he had lead you to a life of crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.05,0:19:33.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, finally, he felt hopeless...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.85,0:19:36.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because he could no longer financially support you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.73,0:19:38.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.81,0:19:41.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chances are...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.31,0:19:44.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's nothing left in this house that can be considered valuable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:46.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.03,0:19:48.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Think about it for a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.86,0:19:51.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In a house as large as this one on such a steep hill...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.49,0:19:56.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would a senile 70 year-old man live all alone,\Nand not hire any servants to help him!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.62,0:19:57.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do you think that is!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.04,0:20:01.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means he had no money left to hire anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.54,0:20:08.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He likely sold all his antiques, and had to\Nmortgage his house along with the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.17,0:20:09.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.51,0:20:12.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the hell is the safe for, then!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.05,0:20:14.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell me what could possibly be in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.64,0:20:15.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm, Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.02,0:20:18.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have opened the safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.73,0:20:19.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.77,0:20:22.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why not go see for yourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.90,0:20:27.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.69,0:20:29.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.11,0:20:31.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're loan contracts...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.49,0:20:35.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys mooched him off, that's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.45,0:20:41.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention your movie production costs,\Nsurf shop costs, and company operation costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.21,0:20:45.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.38,0:20:46.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.71,0:20:47.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all over...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.08,0:20:58.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.06,0:21:00.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could this be of you three?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.93,0:21:02.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.39,0:21:02.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.85,0:21:05.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From when Mom was still alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.52,0:21:07.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.90,0:21:09.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's so nostalgic...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.40,0:21:29.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This photo...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.76,0:21:32.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is what Hisaemon{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} left behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.97,0:21:35.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His final inheritance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.14,0:21:38.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The happy memories you shared as a family...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.14,0:21:41.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're all present in that one photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.52,0:21:48.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, none of you were able to inherit that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.36,0:21:52.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.11,0:21:55.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.45,0:23:29.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm glad about our family, since we don't have\Nto worry about fighting over inheritance.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.67,0:23:31.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.71,0:23:34.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is it, this is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.25,0:23:35.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.76,0:23:37.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, pretty lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.34,0:23:41.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please grab me all these sake bottles!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.30,0:23:42.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.22,0:23:43.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.22,0:23:45.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.68,0:23:46.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.73,0:23:48.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm buying sake for souvenirs!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.23,0:23:51.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's just for a souvenir, just buy one bottleâ€”one bottle!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.19,0:23:52.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be so stingy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.44,0:23:57.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There won't be any inheritance left at this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.37,0:24:01.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kamou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.87,0:24:05.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was innocent, but I suspected him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.99,0:24:07.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By pressuring him...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.33,0:24:08.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I caused his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.45,0:24:47.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conant's Hint
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.41,0:24:49.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Flashlight
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.77,0:24:51.65,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Dad's probably going to give up being a detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.68,0:24:52.73,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,What'd you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.75,0:24:53.80,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is!?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.81,0:24:55.80,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Don't yell...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.72,0:24:55.05,Signs,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode
